      "content": "it doesn't feel like healing anymore though. that's the thing. doctors just keep giving me more meds that don't work and the pain just stays the same or gets worse. it feels so pointless. sometimes i just sit here thinking about how much easier it would be if everything just... stopped. if i could just find some actual peace and not have to deal with this every single second.",
